      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Presented in showroom condition, it features an unblemished exterior and a cabin that retains its original factory luster. Meticulously maintained and strictly garaged, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing short of perfection. Every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards of excellence.",
